5
00:00:39,160 --> 00:00:42,200
♪Rasa rindu yang telah menumpuk♪

6
00:00:43,120 --> 00:00:46,440
♪Semakin bertambah kuat♪

7
00:00:47,220 --> 00:00:52,960
♪Cahaya bulan
menerangi bahu kita♪

8
00:00:53,360 --> 00:00:56,640
♪Meskipun kita terpisah♪

9
00:00:57,000 --> 00:01:01,440
♪Namun, hati kita selalu bersama♪

10
00:01:05,080 --> 00:01:07,280
♪Sambil mengingat masa lalu♪

11
00:01:07,280 --> 00:01:12,440
♪Aku mencari keberadaanmu
